cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the task of video prediction using a GAN model with spatio-temporal 3D convolutions. This task falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of progressively growing GANs, which is a popular technique in the field of generative models (cs.AI). Additionally, the experiments are conducted on video datasets (cs.MM) and the model is trained using adversarial loss (cs.NE).
